        <num>36-13-8</num>
        <content>
          <p>Before enacting any of the codes, rules, or regulations permitted in this chapter, the county governing authority shall hold a public hearing thereon. At least 15 days' notice of the time and place of the hearing shall be published in a newspaper of general circulation in the county.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1961, p. 560, ยง 7.)</p>
